{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/17-fakta-unik-tentang-film-spirited-away/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"17 Fakta Unik Tentang Film Spirited Away yang Harus Kamu Tau!","content":"\n<p>Gimana, udah puas ngerasain film Spirited Away di bioskop sungguhan? Pasti dong, karena fiim ini ngehits banget di awal pertama rilisnya tahun 2009. Dengan pendapatan lebih dari 30 miliyar yen, film Spirited Away adalah film terlaris dalam sejarah Jepang. Film ini bahkan ngalahin Titanic sebagai <em>box office</em>. Padahal nih ya, film ini cuma butuh anggaran dana produksi sekitar 1,9 miliyar yen. Keren ga sih? Mau tahu lebih banyak lagi tentang karya Ghibli yang satu ini? Ya udah, nih kita kasih.</p>\n\n\n\n<iframe width=\"1280\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ByXuk9QqQkk\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n\n\n<h2>Fakta Unik dibalik Spirited Away:</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1.Spirited Away Diproduksi Tanpa Naskah Cerita</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Setelah diwawancara, Miyazaki ternyata ngaku kalau film ini memang tidak punya naskah! “Saya tidak punya bahan cerita apapun ketika kami mulai mengerjakan film ini,” kata Miyazaki kepada Midnight Eye. “Saya tidak sempat membuatnya. Jadi, ceritanya berkembang ketika saya mulai menggambar storyboard. Produksi dimulai tepat setelahnya, ketika pengembangan storyboard masih berjalan.” Miyazaki lebih suka kalau plot cerita berkembang secara organik, sambil berkomentar, “Bukan saya yang menulis filmnya. Film ini menulis dirinya sendiri dan saya tidak punya pilihan selain mengikuti.” Oke, Pak. Bapak Miyazaki masih keren, kok.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image wp-image-1840 size-full\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1840\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/17-fakta-unik-tentang-film-spirited-away/attachment/01/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/01.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/01-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/01.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/01.jpg\" alt=\"Spirited Away - Tanpa Naskah\" class=\"wp-image-1840\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/01.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/01-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Beyond The Cartoon</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2. Miyazaki Adalah Auteur Dari Spirited Away</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hayao Miyazaki menulis, mengarahkan, dan mendesain film Spirited Away. Dia juga sering berpartisipasi dalam animasi tiap frame. Gara-gara ini Miyazaki sering disebut sebagai auteur. Istilah ini berasal dari bahasa Perancis dan biasa digunakan untuk menyebut seorang seniman yang punya kendali besar di setiap bidang produksi film. Nyatanya, ngga semua orang bisa jadi auteur dalam dunia film. Dipikir gampang ngatur ini-itu sambil masih mikirin produksi? Susah, lho. Tapi Miyazaki bisa. Ruar biasa, Pak!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3. Inspirasi Tokoh Spirited Away Datang Dari Liburan Pensiun</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Rupanya karakter utama Spirited Away, Chihiro, terinspirasi dari anak orang. Setelah Miyazaki mengumumkan pensiunnya (semi-permanen) di tahun 1997, kreator kondang ini menghabiskan waktu di sebuah pondok liburan bersama teman-temannya. Kebetulan, temannya Miyazaki ini sekalian bawa anaknya juga, yang—kebetulan lagi nih—membuat Miyazaki pingin bikin film tentang anak-anak biasa yang sepantaran. Dia merasa konten yang khusus dibuat untuk anak umur sepuluh tahunan ngga banyak, dan manga-manga Jepang biasanya cuma fokus ke arah <em>romance </em>dan gebetan. “Saya merasa, [pacaran] bukanlah sesuatu yang bisa mereka pegang, atau yang mereka dambakan,” Miyazaki mengingat-ingat. “Jadi saya berandai-andai membuat film di mana anak-anak biasa ini bisa jadi pahlawan.” Karena itu, Chihiro dikembangkan berdasarkan ingatan Miyazaki tentang gadis kecil yang ditemuinya di pondok itu. “Tiap kali saya menulis atau menggambar sesuatu yang berkaitan dengan Chihiro, saya terus bertanya, apakah anak teman saya itu akan melakukan ini? Atau apa dia akan melakukan itu?”</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image wp-image-1841 size-full\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1841\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/17-fakta-unik-tentang-film-spirited-away/attachment/02/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/02.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/02-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/02.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/02.jpg\" alt=\"Spirited Away - Inspirasi Tokoh\" class=\"wp-image-1841\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/02.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/02-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Studio Ghibli</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ini malah nambah pertanyaan, deh. Apa ayah Chihiro juga terinspirasi dari ayah anak-anak yang jadi inspirasi Miyazaki? Jawabannya: iya.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image wp-image-1842 size-full\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1842\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/17-fakta-unik-tentang-film-spirited-away/attachment/03/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/03.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/03-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/03.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/03.jpg\" alt=\"Spirited Away - Makan\" class=\"wp-image-1842\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/03.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/03-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Studio Ghibli</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4. Miyazaki Bukan Penggemar Majalah Shoujo</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebelum mulai mengerjakan Spirited Away, Miyazaki berusaha membaca majalah shoujo dan majalah lain yang ditargetkan untuk gadis kecil. Niatnya sih mau cari inspirasi. Ujung-ujungnya, Miyazaki malah berpendapat kalau majalah-majalah itu sama sekali tidak membantu.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>5. Detil-detil Kecil Bikin Film Ini Jadi Besar</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalau kamu perhatikan, film Spirited Away memuat banyak sekali detil-detil kecil yang sering terlewat mata. Tapi, detil-detil kecil ini yang menyumbang sensasi ‘nyata’ dan bikin film ini jadi karya seni yang kaya dengan kehidupan. Contohnya? Kamu bisa lihat tanah yang menempel di sol sepatu Chihiro, cahaya dari pantulan resleting, Chihiro yang memakai sepatunya sambil diketuk-ketuk di tanah, sampai kebiasaan Chihiro yang tidak menjawab pertanyaan orangtua sampai ditanyai dua kali! Malah, katanya, salah satu kru film ini bilang supaya Chihiro jangan menjawab sampai ditanyai tiga kali. Mau sedetil apa sih kalian, Ghibli? Iya, anak umur segitu nyebelin, tapi ngga sampai segitunya!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>6. Ngga Di Jepang Ngga di Indonesia, Sungai Kotor Tuh Sama Aja</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingat roh sungai yang butuh bantuan Chihiro untuk mengeluarkan sepeda dari tubuhnya? Ternyata, inspirasinya (lagi-lagi) dari dunia nyata. “Saya pernah membersikan sungai,” kata Miyazaki. “Dekat rumah. Dan di sana benar-benar ada sepeda. Tertancap di sana. Butuh sepuluh orang untuk menambatkan tali di antara setangnya dan menariknya pelan-pelan. Kami benar-benar membuat sungai itu bersih dan ikan-ikannya kembali lagi. Itulah kenapa saya harus menambahkan adegan itu.”</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image wp-image-1843 size-full\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1843\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/17-fakta-unik-tentang-film-spirited-away/attachment/04/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/04.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: Studio Ghibli&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/04-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/04.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/04.jpg\" alt=\"Spirited Away - Nenek seram\" class=\"wp-image-1843\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/04.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/04-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Studio Ghibli</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>7. Pengisi Suara Chihiro Ternyata&#8230; Anak Kecil</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ini adalah film pertama di bawah arahan Miyazaki yang tokoh anak kecilnya disuarakan oleh anak kecil betulan (kayak ada yang palsu aja). Rumi Hiiragi namanya. Kalau kalian jeli, kartu di buket bunga Chihiro ditulis dari ‘sahabat baikmu, Rumi’.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image wp-image-1844 size-full\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1844\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/17-fakta-unik-tentang-film-spirited-away/attachment/05/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/05.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: Studio Ghibli&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/05-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/05.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/05.jpg\" alt=\"Spirited Away - Bunga\" class=\"wp-image-1844\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/05.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/05-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Studio Ghibli</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>8. Adegan-adegan Sunyi Rupanya Penuh Makna</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Adegan-adegan ‘diam’, misalnya saat ada tokoh yang memandang di kejauhan, atau duduk berpikir, rupanya sengaja (dan sering) dimasukkan oleh Miyazaki. Ini dinamakan “ma”, yang berarti “kekosongan” dalam bahasa Jepang. Dalam sebuah wawancara, Miyazaki menjelaskan manfaat adegan-adegan ini. “Kalau Anda hanya menyuguhkan <em>action</em> nonstop tanpa ada ruang untuk bernapas, semua itu hanya dengung kesibukan. Tapi jika Anda berhenti sebentar, ketegangan yang dibangun dalam film bisa terangkat ke dimensi yang lebih lebar.” Jika 80% film hanya diisi klimaks dan ketegangan, lanjutnya, kamu hanya akan mati rasa.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image wp-image-1845 size-full\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1845\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/17-fakta-unik-tentang-film-spirited-away/attachment/06/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/06.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: Studio Ghibli&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/06-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/06.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/06.jpg\" alt=\"Spirited Away - Laut\" class=\"wp-image-1845\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/06.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/06-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Studio Ghibli</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>9. Pixar dan Ghibli Berteman Baik</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Iya, kemarin sih Toshio Suzuki, produser Spirited Away, bilang Disney ‘tidak kreatif’. Tapi di balik itu, rupanya kedua studio ini punya hubungan yang cukup baik! Kepala Kreatif Pixar, John Lasseter, suka banget sama film ini. Dia sampai bikin penayangan Spirited Away yang pertama di luar Jepang, di Studio Pixar. Miyazaki juga meminta bantuannya untuk mengomandoi prosesi dubbing bahasa Inggris untuk Spirited Away.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image wp-image-1846 size-full\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1846\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/17-fakta-unik-tentang-film-spirited-away/attachment/07/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/07.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: Beyond The Cartoon&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/07-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/07.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/07.jpg\" alt=\"Spirited Away - Kakek\" class=\"wp-image-1846\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/07.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/07-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Beyond The Cartoon</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Banyak studio yang sudah siap ancang-ancang untuk membeli hak distribusi film Ghibli, tapi Toshio Suzuki selalu menolak. Gosipnya, mereka cukup trauma dengan adaptasi Nausicaä yang terlalu diubah sampai kehilangan inti filmnya. Pada akhirnya Disney berhasil menggandeng Ghibli dengan tawaran khusus: janji bahwa mereka tidak akan pernah mengubah isi film apapun, demi hak distribusi semua film Ghibli. Deal!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Eh, sebentar. Kalian pikir Pixar dan Ghibli baru berteman setelah Spirited Away? Salah! Sebelum itu mereka sudah akrab, lho. Inget si lampu yang lompat-lompat menyambut Chihiro di gerbang Zeniba? Yak, itu referensi logo Pixar, si Luxo!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image wp-image-1847 size-full\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1847\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/17-fakta-unik-tentang-film-spirited-away/attachment/08/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/08.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"08\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/08-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/08.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/08.jpg\" alt=\"Spirited Away - No face\" class=\"wp-image-1847\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/08.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/08-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Studio Ghibli</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>10. Animator Ghibli Juga Manusia</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk membantu para animator Jepang dalam memahami gerakan karakter, Miyazaki sering menggunakan analogi gerakan binatang. Ketika menjelaskan adegan di mana Haku yang terluka jatuh ke perangkap, Miyazaki mendeskripsikan Haku mirip naga yang menempel ke dinding seperti cicak, sebelum jatuh ke tanah seperti ular. Ketika Chihiro menyuapkan obat ke mulut Haku, Miyazaki meminta para animator untuk mencontoh mulut anjing. Ketika Miyazaki mendapati bahwa seluruh animatornya tidak ada yang memelihara anjing, mereka pergi ke dokter hewan sambil bawa kamera.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image wp-image-1848 size-full\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1848\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/17-fakta-unik-tentang-film-spirited-away/attachment/09/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/09.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"09\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/09-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/09.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/09.jpg\" alt=\"Spirited Away - Monster\" class=\"wp-image-1848\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/09.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/09-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Studio Ghibli</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>11. Kamu Bisa Mengunjungi Setting Spirited Away Di Dunia Nyata</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Serius. Jalanan film Spirited Away yang rame dan pemandiannya yang khas rupanya diambil dari dunia nyata. Dateng aja ke Juifen, Taiwan. Di sana, kamu bisa menikmati pemandangan yang familiar dan ramenya kota dunia gaib&#8230; ngga gaib juga ding, tapi mirip! Konon, Miyazaki pernah mengunjungi kedai teh yang populer di sini. Kalau kamu punya rencana ke Taiwan, ajak-ajak penulisnya juga dong. Pengen nih ke sana!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1DRn575pu8o\" width=\"620\" height=\"345\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>12. Soundtrack Spirited Away Sudah Ada Sebelum Filmnya Dibuat</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Lagu penutup Spirited Away (&#8220;Itsumo Nando Demo&#8221;/&#8221;Always With Me&#8221;) dibuat oleh Joe Hisaishi untuk Hayao Miyazaki, jauh sebelum Miyazaki punya ide untuk membuat film Spirited Away. Miyazaki memutarnya berulang-ulang saat mengerjakan film ini dan memutuskan untuk memasukkannya ke <em>end credit</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image wp-image-1849 size-full\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1849\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/17-fakta-unik-tentang-film-spirited-away/attachment/10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/10.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"10\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: Hibiki Hajime&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/10-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/10.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/10.jpg\" alt=\"Spirited Away - Botak\" class=\"wp-image-1849\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/10.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/10-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Hibiki Hajime</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>13. Permen Bintang Makanan Susuwatari Ternyata Punya Nama</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cemilan berbentuk bintang yang disukai Susuwatari (abu hitam) adalah salah satu permen Jepang tradisional yang disebut kompeitô.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image wp-image-1850 size-full\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1850\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/17-fakta-unik-tentang-film-spirited-away/attachment/11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"11\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/11-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/11.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/11.jpg\" alt=\"Spirited Away - Permen Binatang\" class=\"wp-image-1850\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/11.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/11-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Studio Ghibli/Beyond The Cartoon</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>14. Kaonashi Didesain Mirip Seperti Ulat</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tokoh Kaonashi sangat mirip ulat sutera, binatang yang penting di budaya Jepang. Kaonashi, seperti ulat sutera, punya wajah putih dengan tanda wajah yang unik, dan di mulutnya berada di bawah tanda tersebut. Dua makhluk ini juga makan terus dan membesar dengan cepat. Di ujung film, Kaonashi mengunjungi Zeniba bersama Sen, dan akhirnya tinggal dengan Zeniba untuk memintal benang.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image wp-image-1851 size-full\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1851\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/17-fakta-unik-tentang-film-spirited-away/attachment/12/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/12.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"12\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/12-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/12.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/12.jpg\" alt=\"Spirited Away - Wibu\" class=\"wp-image-1851\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/12.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/12-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Studio Ghibli/Beyond The Cartoon</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>15. [SPOILER!] Ending Spirited Away Rupanya Seperti Ini</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Miyazaki mengungkap, setelah pergi dari pemandian, Chihiro sama sekali tidak ingat tentang petualangannya. Atau tentang Haku.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image wp-image-1852 size-full\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1852\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/17-fakta-unik-tentang-film-spirited-away/attachment/13/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/13.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"13\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: Studio Ghibli&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/13-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/13.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/13.jpg\" alt=\"Spirited Away - anak cewek\" class=\"wp-image-1852\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/13.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/13-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Studio Ghibli</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>16. Banyak Adegan Spirited Away Yang Dipotong</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Saat menyelesaikan film ini, Miyazaki sadar bahwa Spirited Away akan memakan waktu lebih dari tiga jam dan terpaksa harus menghapus beberapa bagian cerita untuk memotong waktu. Dia mengaku, ini adalah bagian terberat dalam pembuatan film Spirited Away.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>17. Chihiro, Kamu Menawan Hatiku</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Miyazaki bertekad untuk menciptakan protagonis dari sosok gadis biasa yang bisa menarik simpati penonton. Katanya, “Ini bukan cerita di mana tokoh-tokohnya tumbuh dewasa, tapi ini cerita di mana mereka menegaskan sesuatu yang sudah ada dalam diri mereka, yang hanya bisa keluar ketika situasinya memaksa.”</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image wp-image-1853 size-full\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1853\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/17-fakta-unik-tentang-film-spirited-away/attachment/14/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/14.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"14\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/14-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/14.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/14.jpg\" alt=\"Spirited Away - Anak kecil\" class=\"wp-image-1853\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/14.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/14-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Studio Ghibli</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Tapi katanya nih, Miyazaki sering frustrasi sendiri ketika mengembangkan Chihiro! Nah, lho. Awalnya Miyazaki tidak ingin Chihiro dianggap ‘cantik’, tapi bapak ini merasa bahwa desain Chihiro terlalu biasa. Sering dia kepikiran, “Chihiro tidak imut. Apa kita tidak bisa melakukan sesuatu?” Tapi, makin dekat dengan akhir cerita, Miyazaki jadi lega. Kenapa? Karena dia merasa bahwa Chihiro akan tumbuh menjadi “wanita yang menawan.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image wp-image-1854 size-full\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1854\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/17-fakta-unik-tentang-film-spirited-away/attachment/15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/15.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"15\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/15-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/15.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/15.jpg\" alt=\"Spirited Away - anak cewek ama monster\" class=\"wp-image-1854\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/15.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/15-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Studio Ghibli</figcaption></figure></div>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"d539aeca-c864-56d9-88fd-e7017422fd81"}}}